2002-1689 (La. 10/14/02)

James Keith BROWN, et al. v. TRINITY UNIVERSAL INSURANCE CO. et al. Patricia Brown, et al. v. Mark F. Beslin, et al. No. 2002-C-1689. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 14, 2002.

In re Brown, James Keith; — Plaintiff; Applying for Writ of Certiorari and/or Review, Parish of Acadia, 15th Judicial District Court Div. K, Nos. 73-705-K, 73-726-B; to the Court of Appeal, Third Circuit, No. 01-1405.

Denied.

KIMBALL, J., would grant the writ. KNOLL, J., would grant the writ.
